It is only in the mysterious equations of love that any logical reasion can be found.

1. it is ..., that...
  强调句
  It is my mom that loves me most in the world. 只有我的妈妈是世界上最爱我的人。
  
  It was probably him who killed Ray for Cheese.很有可能是他替奶酪杀了雷。
  
2. mysterious equations of love  神秘的爱情等式。
  
3. logical reasion 合理的理由

  Make it a habit to replace each negative thought with a logical reason. 打消每个消极的念头，找到合理的理由，将之形成习惯。
